Tomorrow,is,an,organization,that,promotes,the,efficient,use,of,energy,resources,The,Tomorrow,CO,Signal,API,provides,carbon,footprint,detection,mechanism,that,makes,it,possible,for,a,smart,device,to,consume,electricity,when,the,carbon,footprint,is,at,its,lowest,It,provides,access,to,information,about,the,source,and,production,procedures,of,electricity,supply,as,well,as,the,quantity,of,carbon,attributable,to,its,production,The,API,sends,requests,and,returns,responses,in,JSON,format